1093.name: AlMg 4.5Mn Tig
1093.Applications: Filler metal for Magnesium and Manganese alloyed Aluminium with a maximum Magnesium content of 5%. This alloy shows very good mechanical properties that make it ideal for applications in shipyards, in car and railway industry and constructions of reservoirs and tanks.
1093.Suitable_For: Aluminium alloys: AlMg4,5Mn, AlMg5, AlMg2Mn0,8, AlZnMg1, AlZnMgCu0,5, AlMgSi0,5, AlMgSi1, G-AlMg10, G-AlMg5, G-AlMg3Si, G-AlMg5Si, 3.3545, 3.3547, 3.3535, 3.3555, 3.3206, 3.3210, 3.2315, 3.3211, 3.4335, EN AW 5086, EN AW 5083, EN AW 5019, EN AW 5019, EN AW 6060, EN AW 6005A, EN AW 6082, EN AW 6061, EN AW 7020, EN AC 51300, EN AC 51400,
